      use RegisterCapabilitiesEvent
      Registers a capability to be consumed by others. APIs who define the capability should call this. To retrieve the Capability instance, use the @CapabilityInject annotation. This method is safe to call during parallel mod loading.
      Parameters:
      type - The class type to be registered
